            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>fresh orecchiette</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>orecchiette</strong> for 4-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
