      "instruction": "<p>Peel and slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>saffron</strong> with 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[425ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>saffron stock</strong></p>",
