      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sausage meat is starting to brown, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and <strong>saffron stock</strong> and cook for 2-3 min further or until the sauce thickens slightly and the sausage meat is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1695653490854-x200.jpg",
