        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, add a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cracked black pepper</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sausage & saffron ragù</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
