        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>drained orecchiette</strong> into the sauce<strong> </strong>and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce, discard the<strong> bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
